message.content: cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DL. The paper discusses information retrieval (IR) systems and their limitations, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also leverages language models and structural knowledge of Wikipedia, which falls under the categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.DL).
